    "updated_at": "2017-03-02T18:17:42Z",
    "body": "@willin I don't think it's possible to adjust the positioning of a MenuItem. To handle the `dev/prod` toggling option, you might consider using the `radio` type or a [`submenu`](https://electron.atom.io/docs/api/menu-item/).\r\n\r\nThere is not a way to add a popup with custom content as in your screenshot above. Your best option would be to open a BrowserWindow containing that content when the user clicks the MenuItem."
